,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:26:06.000Z","msg":"林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462e9a83f27121ee7c02b47889debda2af8e3e22","tid":46372,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>方文山好堆砌詞藻<br />\n<br />\n意境同表達一定係林夕，仲要粵語難填咁多<br />\n佢填國語又得，得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n林夕真係好勁 弱水三千 夕陽無限好 開到荼蘼真係好有feel 聽左好多年"},{"pid":"f8d73729ea20199779beea6d4ed2196c621566c4","tid":46372,"uid":21254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:27:36.000Z","msg":"林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639ba72149ede4a2485805589d90b5fe9cbeaf34","tid":46372,"uid":22895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea5b4dc750959c5e58641858119c6e310555c867","tid":46372,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係一首浮誇已經不得了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e89deeaec4546ce91dd1042b4dfefb17328870","tid":46372,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗夕爺，講內容講意境林若寧都拋方文山幾條街啦老實</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真"},{"pid":"269ff73e5302725360f26767ede57af234f00133","tid":46372,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗夕爺，講內容講意境林若寧都拋方文山幾條街啦老實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夕爺啲詞的確好有意境 同埋佢好多詞都要慢慢品味<br />\n加上廣東詞真係難寫 所以我都正皮林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過方文山啲詞真係好靚好華麗 加上佢有填中國風（有好文學feel)"},{"pid":"e708a1b36ec52faef161cb940a784954bc1c6625","tid":46372,"uid":32298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:44:46.000Z","msg":"夕爺啦，仲洗問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c718cdb486b04a2412c8c4353d039a34546a3652","tid":46372,"uid":17984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:58:48.000Z","msg":"林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  啲歌好正 <br />\n不過我都幾鍾意方文山中國風既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}